OL,3,CPedestrian left with serious injuries
OL,4,Cafter being struck by car
OL,6,FPolice in Lancashire are appealing for
OL,7,Fwitnesses after a man in his 40s was
OL,8,Fstruck by a car on Saturday night
OL,9,F(23rd May).
OL,11,FOfficers were called shortly after 9pm
OL,12,Fto reports that an Audio Q4 Etron had
OL,13,Fcollided with a pedestrian on Church
OL,14,FBank Street in Darwen.
OL,16,FThe man was taken to hospital with a
OL,17,Fnumber of serious injuries but he's
OL,18,Fbeen described as being in a stable
OL,19,Fcondition.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/3
