OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1779696396
OL,3,CPedestrian left with serious injuries
OL,4,Cafter being struck by car
OL,6,FThe driver of the Audi, a 28-year-old
OL,7,Fman from Old Langho, was arrested at
OL,8,Fthe scene on suspicion of causing
OL,9,Fserious injury by dangerous driving.
OL,10,FHe remains in custody.
OL,12,FSgt Joe Calvert, from our Road
OL,13,FPolicing Unit, said: "This collision
OL,14,Fhas left a man with a number of
OL,15,Fsignificant injuries and my thoughts
OL,16,Fare with him and his loved ones at
OL,17,Fthis time.
OL,19,F"Work is ongoing to establish the full
OL,20,Fcircumstances which led to the
OL,21,Fcollision.
OL,26,@uD@VOU{D@AOU
