PN,39403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1779696396
OL,3,CPedestrian left with serious injuries
OL,4,Cafter being struck by car
OL,6,F"We know there were a number of people
OL,7,Fin the area attending the local music
OL,8,Ffestival who potentially saw what
OL,9,Fhappened or captured the incident on
OL,10,Fmobile phone footage.
OL,12,F"We want to hear from them as soon as
OL,13,Fpossible. We would also ask that
OL,14,Fanyone with CCTV or dashcam footage
OL,15,Fwhich could help us with our enquiries
OL,16,Fto contact the police as soon as
OL,17,Fpossible."
